Paper: hep-th/9710197

Date: 1997-10-26

Title: SD Perturbiner in YM+Gravity

Authors: K.Selivanov

Comments: 8 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B420 (1998) 274-278

An explicit self-dual classical solution of the type of perturbiner inYang-Mills theory interacting with gravity is obtained. This allows one todescribe the tree self-dual gluonic form-factors including any number ofpositive-helicity gravitons in addition to the positive helicity gluons.